_:N25d15be6456e42948aec18cd35f80261 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Richard Hermer was appointed Attorney General on 5 July 2024.</p>\n\n<p>Richard Hermer KC was called to the Bar in 1993 and he took silk in 2009. He was previously Head of Chambers at Matrix and has served as a Deputy High Court Judge. </p>\n\n" .
